tomated emails after purchases, and recover abandoned carts to drive more sales with Reach'=>'通过 Reach 在结账时收集联系人信息、在购买后自动发送电子邮件以及恢复放弃的购物车，从而提高销售额','Coming soon'=>'即将推出','Connect'=>'连接','Connect domain'=>'连接域','Connect Hostinger Reach to start Email Marketing'=>'连接Hostinger Reach，开始电子邮件营销','Connect Now'=>'立即连接','Connect plugin'=>'连接插件','Connect site'=>'连接网站','Connect WooCommerce'=>'连接 WooCommerce','Connect WooCommerce to boost sales with email automations'=>'连接 WooCommerce，利用电子邮件自动化提高销售额','Contact Form 7'=>'联系表单 7','Contacts'=>'联系方式','contacts'=>'联系人','Contacts to Import'=>'要导入的联系人','Could not generate auth URL'=>'无法生成验证 URL','Create a new form or connect a plugin to grow your contact list and start sending campaigns with Reach.'=>'创建一个新表单或连接一个插件来增加联系人列表，并开始使用 Reach 发送营销活动。','Create campaign'=>'创建活动','Create fully custom forms in Reach and easily embed them on your WordPress site using this plugin. Stay tuned!'=>'使用此插件在 Reach 中创建完全自定义的表单，并轻松将其嵌入到 WordPress 网站中。敬请期待！','Create template'=>'创建模板','Default'=>'默认值','Disconnect'=>'断开','Disconnect it to link this site instead.'=>'断开连接，转而链接本网站。','Disconnect plugin'=>'断开插件','Disconnect plugin?'=>'是否断开插件？','Disconnecting will stop new contacts from being collected. You can reconnect or use a different form anytime.'=>'断开连接将停止收集新的联系人。您可以随时重新连接或使用其他表单。','Don\'t see your plugin?'=>'没有看到您的插件？','E-Commerce'=>'电子商务','Easily add or connect existing forms, automate WooCommerce, and sync contacts to start building campaigns and grow your business.'=>'轻松添加或连接现有表单、自动执行 WooCommerce 和同步联系人，即可开始建立营销活动并发展业务。','Edit form'=>'编辑表单','Elementor'=>'元素','Email'=>'电子邮件','Email marketing background with gradient design'=>'具有渐变设计的电子邮件营销背景','Email marketing illustration featuring envelopes and communication icons'=>'以信封和通信图标为特色的电子邮件营销插图','Email marketing that doesn\'t need an expert: Let AI write, design, and send your campaigns - your brand, your colors, applied automatically. No coding, no complexity.'=>'无需专家的电子邮件营销：让人工智能来撰写、设计和发送您的营销活动--自动应用您的品牌、颜色。无需编码，没有复杂性。','Emails'=>'电子邮件','Enter tag name and press Enter or click Add Tag'=>'输入标签名称并按 Enter 或点击添加标签','Expand {pluginName} details'=>'展开 {pluginName} 的详细信息','FAQ'=>'常见问题','Form'=>'形式','Form Builder'=>'表格生成器','Form ID'=>'表单 ID','Forminator'=>'Forminator','Forms'=>'表单','Forms syncing with Reach'=>'与 Reach 同步表单','Go to plugin'=>'转到插件','Go to Reach'=>'转到Reach','Hostinger'=>'Hostinger','Hostinger Reach'=>'Hostinger Reach','Hostinger Reach is a Hostinger service that helps you create and send branded email campaigns in minutes with smart AI tools. Hostinger Reach WordPress Plugin allows you to connect and sync contacts from your favorite WordPress plugins into Reach.'=>'Hostinger Reach是Hostinger的一项服务，利用智能人工智能工具帮助您在几分钟内创建和发送品牌电子邮件。Hostinger Reach WordPress插件允许您将最喜欢的WordPress插件中的联系人连接并同步到Reach中。','Hostinger Reach is an AI-powered email marketing tool for small businesses and creators. It supports your entire email marketing journey—from building contact lists to sending campaigns and tracking results.'=>'Hostinger Reach是一款面向小型企业和创作者的人工智能电子邮件营销工具。它支持整个电子邮件营销过程--从建立联系人列表到发送营销活动和跟踪结果。','Hostinger Reach is built for simplicity, speed, and results – no design or marketing experience needed. Unlike most email tools, at the core of Reach is its AI-powered template creator. Whether it is a product launch, special offer, or newsletter update, it instantly crafts a professional, mobile-friendly email. It not only writes the content for you; it also suggests the best layout for your message and saves your style settings so you\'re never starting from scratch.<br><br>Every template is customizable, so your emails reflect your brand\'s look, feel, and voice. And because the templates are built using proven best practices, they\'re optimized for readability, accessibility, and reader engagement.'=>'Hostinger Reach简单、快速、高效，无需设计或营销经验。与大多数电子邮件工具不同，Reach的核心是其AI驱动的模板创建器。无论是产品发布、特别优惠还是时事通讯更新，它都能立即制作出专业、移动友好的电子邮件。它不仅能为您编写内容，还能为您的信息提出最佳布局建议，并保存您的风格设置，让您无需从头开始。<br><br>每个模板都可自定义，因此您的电子邮件都能反映出您的品牌外观、感觉和声音。此外，由于这些模板是采用经过验证的最佳实践构建的，因此它们在可读性、可访问性和读者参与度方面都得到了优化。','Hostinger Reach Logo'=>'霍斯廷格-里奇标志','Hostinger Reach requires minimum PHP version of <b>%s</b>. '=>'Hostinger Reach要求最低PHP版本<b>%s</b>。','How are segments and tags created?'=>'如何创建分段和标记？','How does contact syncing work?'=>'如何同步联系人？','How is Hostinger Reach different from other email marketing apps?'=>'Hostinger Reach与其他电子邮件营销应用程序有何不同？','How much does it cost to use Hostinger Reach?'=>'使用Hostinger Reach的费用是多少？','How would you rate your experience with Hostinger Reach so far?'=>'您如何评价您在Hostinger Reach的经历？','https://hostinger.com'=>'https://hostinger.com','https://www.hostinger.com/email-marketing'=>'https://www.hostinger.com/email-marketing','If the integration is interrupted, syncing pauses automatically. Once the connection is restored, syncing resumes, so you can continue collecting contacts without losing data.'=>'如果整合中断，同步会自动暂停。一旦恢复连接，同步就会恢复，这样你就可以继续收集联系人，而不会丢失数据。','If your store isn’t ready yet, complete the setup to start selling and collecting contacts'=>'如果您的商店尚未准备就绪，请完成设置以开始销售和收集联系人信息','Import'=>'进口','Import Contacts'=>'导入联系人','Import contacts'=>'导入联系人','Import your existing contacts to Reach'=>'将现有联系人导入 Reach','Imported'=>'进口','Importing is not available for this integration'=>'此集成不提供导入功能','Importing...'=>'导入...','Inactive'=>'未激活','Inline'=>'内联','Install'=>'安装','Install and connect'=>'安装和连接','Installed plugins'=>'已安装的插件','Integrate your WordPress site with Hostinger Reach.'=>'将您的WordPress网站与Hostinger Reach整合。','Integrations'=>'集成','It may not be supported yet. You can upload contacts as a CSV or use another plugin'=>'可能还不支持。您可以以 CSV 格式上传联系人信息，或使用其他插件','It was an error importing your contacts to Reach.'=>'将联系人同步到 Reach 时出现错误。','Layout'=>'布局','Layout Settings'=>'布局设置','Learn more'=>'了解更多','Make sure the people you contact expect your emails and are okay with receiving them.'=>'确保联系人希望收到您的电子邮件，并同意接收。','Manage'=>'管理','Manage automations'=>'管理自动化','Manage plugin'=>'管理插件','More plugins'=>'更多插件','Name'=>'名称','New contact form'=>'新的联系表单','New page'=>'新页面','New subscribers'=>'新用户','New Tag Name'=>'新标签名称','Ninja Forms'=>'忍者表格','No'=>'没有','No forms found for this integration.'=>'未找到该整合的表格。','No pages available. Create a new page to get started.'=>'没有可用页面。创建新页面。','Not imported'=>'未进口','Not needed'=>'不需要','of'=>'的','Once you connect a form plugin you use on WordPress (such as Elementor or Contact Form 7), the plugin automatically forwards all the new form submissions and subscriber data to your Reach account, so your contacts are collected and updated without manual exports on each form submission'=>'一旦您连接了 WordPress 上使用的表单插件（如 Elementor 或 Contact Form 7），该插件就会自动将所有新提交的表单和订阅者数据转发到您的 Reach 账户，这样您就可以收集和更新联系人信息，而无需在每次提交表单时手动导出。','opens in new tab'=>'在新标签页打开','OptinMonster'=>'OptinMonster','or connect a form plugin'=>'或连接表单插件','Partially imported'=>'部分进口','Plan & Limits'=>'计划与限制','Plugin'=>'插件','Plugin connected successfully'=>'插件连接成功','Plugin disconnected successfully'=>'插件成功断开连接','Purchases'=>'采购','Reach automatically tags synced contacts using the form name and also creates a segment for easier targeting. If the form doesn’t have a title, it uses the form location title. As a final fallback, the tag title will be the plugin name.If you create a form using Hostinger Reach option, you can also assign multiple existing or new tags to subscribers. Each form will automatically generate its own segment in Reach dashboard, making it easy to send campaigns to specific audiences — and you can fully manage or create additional segments anytime in Reach.'=>'Reach 会使用表单名称自动标记同步的联系人，并创建一个分段以方便定位。如果表单没有标题，它会使用表单位置标题。如果使用 Hostinger Reach 选项创建表单，还可以为订阅者分配多个现有或新标签。每个表单都会在Reach仪表板中自动生成自己的细分市场，这样就可以轻松地向特定受众发送营销活动--您还可以随时在Reach中全面管理或创建其他细分市场。','Reach is already connected to another site.'=>'Reach 已连接到另一个站点。','Reach offers a <b>free plan</b> for one year– perfect for getting started. Paid plans are based on how many unique contacts you aim to reach and how many emails you send monthly. As your audience grows, you can upgrade to a plan that fits your needs. Reach does not limit your contact list, so you don\'t need to worry about lost data and can consistently grow your audience.'=>'Reach 提供为期一年的免费套餐，非常适合新手入门。付费套餐根据触达的联系人数量以及每月发送电子邮件数量而定。随着受众的增加，您可以升级到更适合您需要的套餐。Reach 不会限制您的联系人列表，因此您不必担心数据丢失，可以持续增加您的受众。','Reach Subscription Form'=>'订阅表格','Remaining'=>'剩余','Review domain'=>'审查领域','Segments'=>'分段','Select page'=>'选择页面','Send newsletters with professionally designed templates, automate campaigns, and build AI-powered segments. With Hostinger Reach, growing your audience is easy.'=>'使用专业设计的模板发送新闻邮件，自动开展营销活动，并建立人工智能支持的细分市场。有了Hostinger Reach，增加受众变得轻而易举。','Sent'=>'已发送','Set up WooCommerce'=>'设置 WooCommerce','Settings'=>'设置','Show Name'=>'节目名称','Show Name Field?'=>'显示名称字段？','Show Surname'=>'显示姓氏','Show Surname Field?'=>'显示姓氏字段？','Something went wrong'=>'出错了','Something went wrong. Please try again.'=>'出错了。请重试。','Status'=>'状态','Store Events'=>'商店活动','Subscribe'=>'订阅','Subscribe to our Newsletter'=>'订阅我们的时事通讯','Subscribe to our newsletter'=>'订阅我们的通讯','Subscribers'=>'订阅者','Subscription form is not available at the moment'=>'暂时没有订阅表格','Supported plugins'=>'查看支持的插件','Sure Forms'=>'确定表格','Surname'=>'姓氏','Sync'=>'同步','Tags'=>'标签','Thanks for subscribing.'=>'感谢您的订阅。','The selected contacts are being imported to Reach.'=>'所选联系人正在同步到 Reach。','This form has not an email field. Create an email field in the form to allow it to be synced with Reach'=>'此表单没有电子邮件字段。请在表单中创建电子邮件字段，以便与 Reach 同步。','This form is a Reach native form inserted directly in your page. For disabling it remove the Form directly from the page using the editor.'=>'该表单是直接插入页面的 Reach 本地表单。要禁用它，请使用编辑器直接从页面中移除表单。','This is a temporary domain. In order to connect WordPress to Reach you need to connect your domain.'=>'这是一个临时域名。要将 WordPress 连接到 Reach，您需要连接您的域名。','This month'=>'本月','Thrive Leads'=>'茁壮成长','Total subscribers'=>'订阅总数','Tracks abandoned carts so you can trigger email automations in Reach when enabled.'=>'跟踪放弃的购物车，启用后可在 Reach 中触发电子邮件自动化。','Tracks purchases so you can trigger email automations in Reach when enabled.'=>'跟踪购买情况，启用后可在 Reach 中触发电子邮件自动发送功能。','Unique identifier for this form'=>'该表格的唯一标识符','Unsubscribes'=>'退订','Upgrade'=>'升级','Upload as CSV'=>'以 CSV 格式上传','usage statistics'=>'使用统计','View form'=>'查看表单','View more supported plugins'=>'查看更多支持的插件','Welcome to Reach'=>'欢迎来到Reach','What happens if the connection breaks?'=>'如果连接中断会发生什么？','What is Hostinger Reach email marketing service?'=>'什么是Hostinger Reach电子邮件营销服务？','What\'s the difference between Hostinger Reach and Hostinger Reach WordPress Plugin?'=>'Hostinger Reach和Hostinger Reach WordPress插件有什么区别？','When syncing is off, collected Contacts will not be sent to Reach.'=>'同步关闭时，收集的通讯录不会发送到 Reach。','Will contacts be added to my email list automatically?'=>'联系人会自动添加到我的电子邮件列表中吗？','WooCommerce'=>'WooCommerce','WooCommerce Customers'=>'WooCommerce 客户','WooCommerce Plugin Connected'=>'已连接 WooCommerce 插件','Would you like to import contacts collected while sync was disabled?'=>'您想同步在同步禁用时收集的联系人吗？','WP Forms Lite'=>'WP 表单精简版','WP Forms Lite %s'=>'WP 表单精简版 %s','WS Form'=>'WS 表格','Yes'=>'是','Yes — new subscribers are added automatically based on your setup. Some integrations may also support importing previously collected contacts (historical data), depending on the plugin and connection flow. You’ll be able to review the available options during setup. You can manage subscriber settings like double opt-in, and adjust or organize segments directly in your Reach dashboard.'=>'是的，新用户会根据您的设置自动添加。某些集成还支持导入以前收集的联系人（历史数据），具体取决于插件和连接流程。您可以在设置过程中查看可用选项。您可以直接在 Reach 面板上管理订阅者设置（如双选）、调整或组织细分。','You are not connected to Hostinger Reach'=>'您没有连接到Hostinger Reach','You are not connected to Hostinger Reach. To gain full access to this block, you need to connect your Hostinger Reach account.'=>'您还没有连接到Hostinger Reach。您需要连接您的Hostinger Reach账户，才能完全访问该区块。','You are running <b>%s</b> PHP version.'=>'您运行的是 <b>%s</b> PHP 版本。','You can import existing contacts into Reach now to use them for your email campaigns. New contacts will be synced automatically to Reach.'=>'您可以立即将现有联系人导入 Reach，用于电子邮件营销活动。新联系人将自动同步到 Reach。','You have not selected any forms to import. Select which forms you want to import and then click on the Import button below.'=>'您尚未选择任何要同步的表单。选择要同步的表格，然后单击下面的同步按钮。','Your domain is not active. In order to connect WordPress to Reach you need to have an active domain.'=>'您的域名未激活。要将 WordPress 连接到 Reach，您需要有一个激活的域。','Your form is ready. Go to Reach to complete setup and create templates.'=>'您的表单已准备就绪。前往 Reach 完成设置并创建模板。','Your site is not connected to Reach. Connect to Reach and try again.'=>'您的网站未连接到 Reach。请连接 Reach 并重试。']];
